| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2020-0020 — Recovery Inhibition (doppelpaymer)"
| comment "Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 4eca7bee-0a45-5d3d-991a-d450c262633e"
